title: Stop Smoking 2012 - Achieve Your New Years Resolution In 2012!
description:
Is your 2012 New Years Resolution to finally quit smoking?  If so, this e-book is for you.  It is short and to the point.  Look no further for ways to quit smoking, meet your 2012 new years resolution! 

This ebook was written to help you quit smoking in 2012.  If you are struggling and haven't had any success in quitting tobacco products then you need this e-book.
